    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks fantastic on the road? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved and maintained\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much as I\u2019ve enjoyed it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
