    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape. It runs like a dream and has been really well-cared for over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, it's ready to go! Come give it a test drive\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I do!",
      "price": 34500.0,
