      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mechanically robust, having undergone essential preventative maintenance including a rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive valve adjustment. The chassis integrity is preserved with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings, ensuring the factory-spec handling remains sharp. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with use, the structural and powertrain components are in excellent operational order. The interior maintains its ergonomic integrity with Nappa leather seating and functional M-series instrumentation.",
